  p PetPal’s Founding Class is comprised of Silicon Valley’s Top Talent. With experience from companies such as Google, Samsung, PayPal, NASA, Yahoo, and Tesla Motors, the team collectively brings outstanding technical, design, and business expertise to the PetPal product. The Founding Class shares in the forward-thinking vision for how PetPal can transform and shape the pet ownership space.
  br
  h4 PetPal Advisor
  h5 Dr. Varsha Ramoutar
  p PetPal believes in the Pet’s perspective. To help us correctly identify and define what that perspective is we have a dedicated Veterinarian to advise our team and help guide our company direction. Our commitment is truly to the pets themselves and our Veterinarian Advisor’s role is to hold us accountable to that commitment, and to ensure our content and information is correct and current. 
